  - section: 1
    lineIndex: 32
    speakerName: Stranger
  choicePanel: {fileID: 1604306687}
  choiceButtons:
  - {fileID: 1426696602}
  - {fileID: 1725586204}
  - {fileID: 1300326814}
  - {fileID: 1011540783}
  choiceButtonLabels:
  - {fileID: 327344070}
  - {fileID: 224567845}
  - {fileID: 1891679652}
  - {fileID: 619485680}
  nextSceneButton: {fileID: 400745357}
  autoNextSceneName: 
  introLines:
  - "\u201EThe cold night air bites at your skin as you leave your home behind.\""
  - "\u201EFor a moment you consider turning back.\""
  - The poison is still waiting on the table for you.
  - The invitation could be a trap...
  - ...or just the drunken ramblings of a madman.
  - Yet... your feet keep moving.
  - The old well is located deep in the forest.
  - So far away from civilization, that only a few villagers ever occasionally visit
    it.
  - The thought of nobody hearing your screams if something were to happen makes
    you deeply uncomfortable.
  - You continue walking.
  - '*Whooshhhh*'
  - The deeper you go - the wind blows stronger and the path grows darker.
  - "\u201CWe offer purpose.\u201D"
  - The words from the note echo in your mind...
  - The stranger somehow knew...
  - Not that you had lost your job, not that you were poor.
  - Something much worse.
  - They knew what you were about to do.
  - ...
  - A faint orange light appears ahead.
  - You immediately stop walking.
  - The light moves between the shadows of the trees.
  - Slowly. Not like somebody is wandering around. But waiting. For you...
  - You take a few steps forward, trying not to make any noise.
  - A tall figure finally emerges from the darkness.
  - The knight with broad shoulders looks at you, while one hand holds a lantern
    and the other is laying on the handle of his sword.
  - His armor is old but meticulously maintained.
  - The flame inside his lantern flickers due to the strong wind.
  - He studies you for a moment.
  - Then he nods.
  - "\u201CAs expected,\u201D"
  - "\u201C...\u201D"
  - "\u201CYou received the invitation.\u201D"
  choices:
  - buttonText: "\u201CYes.\u201D"
    resultLines:
    - The knight nods.
    - "\u201CThen follow me\u201D"
    - 'You would have expected more of a warm welcome, but you decide to just see

      what
      will happen next.'
    speakerChanges:
    - lineIndex: 0
      speakerName: YOU
    - lineIndex: 1
      speakerName: Stranger
    - lineIndex: 2
      speakerName: YOU
  - buttonText: '"Who are you?"'
    resultLines:
    - The knight smirks discreetly.
    - "\u201CI\u2019m Brother Garrick.\u201D"
    - "\u201CNow let\u2019s not waste any more time...\u201D"
    - "\u201CFollow my lead.\u201D"
    speakerChanges:
    - lineIndex: 0
      speakerName: YOU
    - lineIndex: 1
      speakerName: Brother Garrick
    - lineIndex: 2
      speakerName: Brother Garrick
    - lineIndex: 3
      speakerName: Brother Garrick
  - buttonText: "\u201CHow did you know I would come?\u201D"
    resultLines:
    - The knight remains silent for several seconds.
    - "\u201CThe hopeless often do.\u201D"
    - Not exactly an answer.
    - The knight starts walking away while gesturing you to follow him.
    - You do.
    speakerChanges:
    - lineIndex: 0
      speakerName: YOU
    - lineIndex: 1
      speakerName: Stranger
    - lineIndex: 2
      speakerName: YOU
    - lineIndex: 3
      speakerName: YOU
    - lineIndex: 3
      speakerName: YOU
  - buttonText: "\u201CInvitation? What is this place?\u201D"
    resultLines:
    - The knight glances forward, his lantern swaying softly.
    - "\u201CHave patience. All shall be revealed in time.\u201D"
    - The response does little to ease your concerns.
    - Before you can question it any longer the knight turns away and starts walking.
    - With more questions than answers, you reluctantly follow.
    speakerChanges:
    - lineIndex: 0
      speakerName: YOU
    - lineIndex: 1
      speakerName: Stranger
    - lineIndex: 2
      speakerName: YOU
    - lineIndex: 3
      speakerName: YOU
    - lineIndex: 3
      speakerName: YOU
  endingLines: []
  typingSpeed: 0.03
